'''凯氏带'''（{{lang|en|Casparian strip}}），橫切面稱為-{zh-hans:凯; zh-tw:卡; zh-hk:嘉;}-氏點（{{lang|en|Casparian dot}}）<ref name="Pandey2001">{{cite book|author=Pandey, B. P.|title=''A Textbook of Botany: Angiosperms''|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DXh0IyQZSacC&pg=PA445|year=2001|publisher=S. Chand Publishing|isbn=978-81-219-0404-9|pages=445|access-date=2021-04-18|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510141253/https://books.google.com/books?id=DXh0IyQZSacC&pg=PA445}}</ref>，是[[維管束植物|維管束植物]]（[[羊齒植物|蕨類]]<ref name="Geldner2013">{{cite journal|last1=Geldner|first1=N.|title=The Endodermis|journal=''Annual Review of Plant Biology''|volume=64|issue=1|year=2013|pages=531–558|issn=1543-5008|doi=10.1146/annurev-arplant-050312-120050}}</ref>
與[[種子植物|種子植物]]）[[根部|根部]]{{le|内皮层|Endodermis}}[[細胞壁|細胞壁]]（径向壁和横向壁）中央的带状增厚區域，其成分主要為[[木質素|木質素]]，宽度随物種不同而異。因卡氏帶不透水，可控制[[皮層_(植物)|皮層]]和[[维管束|维管束]]之间的[[蒸散流|水分與無機鹽运输]]，阻止水分與無機鹽經[[質外體|質外體]]運送至{{le|中柱 (植物)|Stele (biology)|中柱}}，使其必須進入[[細胞膜|細胞膜]]內改以[[共質體途徑|共質體途徑]]前往中柱，故有阻擋細胞內外物質運輸的作用，功能與動物組織中的[[緊密連接|緊密連接]]類似<ref name=Current2013>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.cell.com/current-biology/pdf/S0960-9822(13)01058-0.pdf|title=Casparian strips|author=Geldner, N.|journal=''Current Biology''|volume=23|year=2013}}</ref><ref name="RoppoloDe Rybel2011"/>。卡氏帶的發育受SHORT-ROOT（SHR）、SCARECROW（SCR）與MYB36等[[轉錄因子|轉錄因子]]以及中柱細胞合成的[[多肽|多肽]][[植物激素|激素]]調控<ref name="pmid30057307"/><ref name="pmid28104889"/>。

==發現==
卡氏帶的發現可回溯至19世紀中葉，對植物根部{{le|内皮层|Endodermis}}認識的進展<ref name="Seago2020">{{cite journal|author=Seago, J. L., Jr.|title=Revisiting the occurrence and evidence of endodermis in angiosperm shoots|journal=''Flora''|year=2020|volume=273|pages=151709|doi=10.1016/j.flora.2020.151709|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0367253020302085|access-date=2021-04-23|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510135951/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0367253020302085}}</ref>。1865年，德国植物学家{{le|羅伯·凯斯伯里|Robert Caspary|羅伯·-{zh-hans:凯; zh-tw:卡; zh-hk:嘉;}-斯伯里}}首次描述了植物根部的{{le|内皮层|Endodermis}}，發現其[[細胞壁|細胞壁]]有加厚的現象，並將其命名為「{{lang|de|Schutzscheide}}」（意指防護套），後來學者將其加厚的部分稱為卡氏帶，即得名自-{zh-hans:凯; zh-tw:卡; zh-hk:嘉;}-斯伯里<ref name="RoppoloDe Rybel2011">{{cite journal|last1=Roppolo|first1=D.|last2=De Rybel|first2=B.|last3=Tendon|first3=V. D.|last4=Pfister|first4=A.|last5=Alassimone|first5=J.|last6=Vermeer|first6=J. E. M.|last7=Yamazaki|first7=M.|last8=Stierhof|first8=Y.-D.|last9=Beeckman|first9=T.|last10=Geldner|first10=N.|title=A novel protein family mediates Casparian strip formation in the endodermis|journal=''Nature''|volume=473|issue=7347|year=2011|pages=380–383|issn=0028-0836|doi=10.1038/nature10070}}</ref><ref name="Grebe2011">{{cite journal|last1=Grebe|first1=M.|title=Unveiling the Casparian strip|journal=''Nature''|volume=473|issue=7347|year=2011|pages=294–295|issn=0028-0836|doi=10.1038/473294a}}</ref>。1870年代文獻中即出現「-{zh-hans:凯; zh-tw:卡; zh-hk:嘉;}-氏點」（{{lang-de|Caspary'schen fleck}}）一詞<ref name="Russow1872">{{cite book|author=Russow, E.|chapter=Rhizocarpeae. I. Axenorgane: A. Stamm: a. Marsilia (Drummondii, elata, salvatrix)|title=''Vergleichende Untersuchungen betreffend die Histiologie (Histiographie und Histiogenie) der vegetativen und Sporen-bildenden Organe und die Entwickelung der Sporen der Leitbündel-Kryptogamen: mit Berücksichtigung der Histiologie der Phanerogamen, ausgehend von der Betrachtung der Marsiliaceen''|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=L1kKAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA11|pages=1–12|year=1872|publisher=Commissionnaires de l'Académie Impériale des sciences|access-date=2021-04-18|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510140023/https://books.google.com/books?id=L1kKAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA11}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|author=Müller, C.|title=Morphologie der Gewebe|journal=''Just's Botanischer Jahresbericht''|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HZ1HAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA267|volume=12|issue=1|year=1884|pages=234-342|access-date=2021-04-18|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510140008/https://books.google.com/books?id=HZ1HAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA267}}</ref>，二十世紀以後則多稱為「卡氏帶」（{{lang-de|Casparyschen streifen}}）。1922年研究人員首度自植物根部分離了卡氏帶以研究其成分<ref>{{cite journal|title=Physiological Studies in Plant Anatomy III. The Structure of the Endodermis in Relation to its Function|author=Priestley, J. H.; North, E. E.|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/2428118?seq=1#metadata_info_tab_contents|journal=''The New Phytologist''|volume=21|issue=3|year=1922|page=113-139|access-date=2021-04-18|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510140029/https://www.jstor.org/stable/2428118?seq=1#metadata_info_tab_contents}}</ref><ref name="SongShen2019">{{cite journal|last1=Song|first1=C.|last2=Shen|first2=W.|last3=Du|first3=L.|last4=Wen|first4=J.|last5=Lin|first5=J.|last6=Li|first6=R.|title=Development and chemical characterization of Casparian strips in the roots of Chinese fir (Cunninghamia lanceolata)|journal=''Trees''|volume=33|issue=3|year=2019|pages=827–836|issn=0931-1890|doi=10.1007/s00468-019-01820-x}}</ref>。

==成分==
凯氏带的化學成分長期有所爭議，-{zh-hans:凯; zh-tw:卡; zh-hk:嘉;}-斯伯里即指出此構造可能為[[木質素|木質素]]或[[木栓質|木栓質]]組成，後來的學者大多認為是木栓質，直到1990年代才有研究在分析數種植物的卡氏帶後，發現木質素才是其主要成分<ref name="pmid22665765">{{cite journal| author=Naseer, S.; Lee, Y.; Lapierre, C.; Franke, R.; Nawrath, C.; Geldner, N.| title=Casparian strip diffusion barrier in Arabidopsis is made of a lignin polymer without suberin. | journal=''Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences'' | year= 2012 | volume= 109 | issue= 25 | pages= 10101-6 | pmid=22665765 | doi=10.1073/pnas.1205726109 | pmc=3382560 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=22665765  }} </ref>，但許多教科書仍未更新<ref name=Current2013/>。內皮層的細胞壁雖富含木栓質，不過此為內皮層次級分化的結果{{Notetag|1=老根中內皮層細胞壁形成木栓質加厚後，其功能從傳輸水分轉為保護植株，可進一步限制水分與無機鹽的通透，僅剩[[通道細胞|通道細胞]]（少數未發生次級分化的內皮層細胞）保留運輸功能，隨著根部的生長，有些植物的老根中會失去通道細胞<ref name="Geldner2013"/>。}}，過去有學者認為卡氏帶的形成即為次級分化的開端，實則兩者無直接關係，卡氏帶在內皮層初級分化後便已形成，且次級分化是由根的弦切面開始，而非卡氏帶所在的橫切面和徑切面<ref name="Geldner2013"/>。

==功能==
凯氏带完全填充了內皮細胞間包含{{le|中膠層 (植物)|Middle lamella|中膠層}}在內的空隙，使兩細胞的細胞壁幾乎融合<ref name="Geldner2013"/>。在植物根部[[蒸散流|水與無機養分的運輸]]中，凯氏带主要影響[[質體外途徑|質體外運輸]]途徑，即水與無機鹽經[[表皮|表皮]]與皮層細胞壁間質傳遞的運輸。水與無機鹽來到內皮層細胞時，因卡氏帶不透水而需轉而通過細胞膜進入細胞內，改以[[共質體途徑|共質體途徑]]運輸才得以到達{{le|中柱 (植物)|Stele (biology)|中柱}}的[[木質部|木質部]]細胞，進而輸往莖葉等其他器官<ref name="Grebe2011"/>。當生長環境不利時，卡氏帶可作為植物細胞與外界的屏障，避免環境中的離子進入或自身離子的流出<ref name="pmid28104889"/>。此外卡氏帶與內皮層的木栓加厚還有阻擋有毒物質或病原入侵，以及防止水分散逸的功能<ref name="pmid25125504">{{cite journal| author=Robbins, N. E.; Trontin, C.; Duan, L.; Dinneny, J. R.| title=Beyond the barrier: communication in the root through the endodermis. | journal=''Plant Physiology'' | year= 2014 | volume= 166 | issue= 2 | pages= 551-9 | pmid=25125504 | doi=10.1104/pp.114.244871 | pmc=4213087 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=25125504  }} </ref>。有研究顯示植物在高鹽的環境下可能會形成更厚的卡氏帶，且在更靠近根尖的區域即有卡氏帶形成，這可能是對環境的一項[[適應|適應]]<ref name="pmid14986139">{{cite journal| author=Karahara, I.; Ikeda, A.; Kondo, T.; Uetake, Y.| title=Development of the Casparian strip in primary roots of maize under salt stress | journal=''Planta'' | year= 2004 | volume= 219 | issue= 1 | pages= 41-7 | pmid=14986139 | doi=10.1007/s00425-004-1208-7 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=14986139  }} </ref><ref name="pmid21904117">{{cite journal| author=Chen, T.; Cai, X.; Wu, X.; Karahara, I.; Schreiber, L.; Lin, J.| title=Casparian strip development and its potential function in salt tolerance. | journal=''Plant Signaling & Behavior'' | year= 2011 | volume= 6 | issue= 10 | pages= 1499-502 | pmid=21904117 | doi=10.4161/psb.6.10.17054 | pmc=3256377 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=21904117  }} </ref>，但相較於內皮層次級分化的木栓壁在高鹽逆境下會大幅加厚，卡氏帶的改變相對較小<ref name="pmid30517104">{{cite journal| author=Palmgren, M.| title=Plant epithelia: What is the role of the mortar in the wall? | journal=''PLOS Biology'' | year= 2018 | volume= 16 | issue= 12 | pages= e3000073 | pmid=30517104 | doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.3000073 | pmc=6296743 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=30517104  }} </ref>。

凯氏带主要位於根的内皮层，不過有些植物在根部皮層外側的{{le|外皮層|exodermis}}<ref name="Evert2006">{{cite book|author=Evert, R. F.|title=''Esau's Plant Anatomy: Meristems, Cells, and Tissues of the Plant Body: Their Structure, Function, and Development''|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0DhEBA5xgbkC|date=2006-08-28|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-0-470-04737-8|page=6|access-date=2021-04-17|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201063527/https://books.google.com/books?id=0DhEBA5xgbkC|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[茎|茎]]或[[叶|叶]]中也有卡氏帶<ref name="Lersten1997">{{cite journal|last1=Lersten|first1=N. R.|title=Occurrence of endodermis with a casparian strip in stem and leaf|journal=''The Botanical Review''|volume=63|issue=3|year=1997|pages=265–272|issn=0006-8101|doi=10.1007/BF02857952}}</ref>，例如[[白皮松|白皮松]]的針葉與[[天竺葵|天竺葵]]的莖中皆有卡氏帶，可能與防止水分散失或病原入侵有關<ref name="WuLin2005">{{cite journal|last1=Wu|first1=X.|last2=Lin|first2=J.|last3=Lin|first3=Q.|last4=Wang|first4=J.|last5=Schreiber|first5=L.|title=Casparian Strips in Needles are More Solute Permeable than Endodermal Transport Barriers in Roots of Pinus bungeana|journal=''Plant and Cell Physiology''|volume=46|issue=11|year=2005|pages=1799–1808|issn=1471-9053|doi=10.1093/pcp/pci194}}</ref><ref name="pmid21239408">{{cite journal| author=Meyer, C. J.; Peterson, C. A.| title=Casparian bands occur in the periderm of Pelargonium hortorum stem and root | journal=''Annals of Botany'' | year= 2011 | volume= 107 | issue= 4 | pages= 591-8 | pmid=21239408 | doi=10.1093/aob/mcq267 | pmc=3064534 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=21239408  }} </ref>。

==發育==
[[File:Discontinuous_Casparian_strip_in_sgn3_mutant.jpg|thumb]]
凯氏带的發育在內皮層細胞充分[[根部延長區|延展]]後開始<ref name="pmid22665765"/><ref name="pmid27551946">{{cite journal| author=Barberon, M.| title=The endodermis as a checkpoint for nutrients | journal=''New Phytologist'' | year= 2017 | volume= 213 | issue= 4 | pages= 1604-1610 | pmid=27551946 | doi=10.1111/nph.14140 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=27551946  }} </ref>，目前已知兩條促進內皮層細胞形成凯氏带的[[訊息傳遞_(生物)|訊息傳遞路徑]]，第一條為[[轉錄因子|轉錄因子]][[SHORT-ROOT|SHORT-ROOT]]（SHR）激活另外兩種轉錄因子{{tsl|en|MYB (gene)|MYB|MYB36}}與[[SCARECROW|SCARECROW]]（SCR），前者可刺激[[卡氏帶蛋白|卡氏帶蛋白]]（casparian strip proteins，CASP1-5）、[[過氧化物酶|過氧化物酶64]]（PER64）及ESB1（enhanced suberin 1）等與卡氏帶發育相關的蛋白表現，後者則影響卡氏帶在內皮層細胞的位置，其突變會導致卡氏帶的位置過於靠近中柱<ref name="pmid30057307">{{cite journal | author=Li, P.; Yu, Q.; Gu, X.; Xu, C.; Qi, S.; Wang, H.| display-authors=etal | title=Construction of a Functional Casparian Strip in Non-endodermal Lineages Is Orchestrated by Two Parallel Signaling Systems in Arabidopsis thaliana | journal=''Current Biology'' | year=2018 | volume=28 | issue=17 | pages=2777-2786.e2 | pmid=30057307 | doi=10.1016/j.cub.2018.07.028 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=30057307 | access-date=2021-04-17 | archive-date=2021-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417074839/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?Db=pubmed&Cmd=Retrieve&list_uids=30057307&dopt=abstractplus | dead-url=no }}</ref>；第二條則為中柱細胞合成的兩種[[多肽|多肽]][[植物激素|激素]][[凯氏带完整因子|凯氏带完整因子]]1與2（casparian strip integrity factor；CIF1-2）與內皮層細胞径向壁和横向壁的GSO1（SGN3）及GSO2受體結合，促使原本散播在細胞中的CASP集中到與將形成卡氏帶的位置對應的[[細胞膜|細胞膜]]區域<ref name="pmid28104889"/>，形成卡氏帶膜結構域（casparian strip membrane domain，CSD），CSD初形成時為數個不連續的區域，GS01受體則環繞在各CSD區域的邊緣，促進CSD融合成一個連續的帶狀區域，即為將要形成卡氏帶的區域<ref name="pmid25233277"/>。

卡氏帶蛋白為[[膜蛋白|膜蛋白]]，彼此間有交互作用，並可再與PER64、ESB1和呼吸爆發氧化酶同源物F（RBOHF）等合成木質素所需的蛋白結合以啟動卡氏帶發育的下游反應<ref name="Geldner2013"/><ref name="RoppoloDe Rybel2011"/>。缺乏GSO1受體或同時缺乏CIF1與CIF2多肽的突變植株中，CASP1在內皮層細胞膜上分布異常，CSD無法正常融合成連續完整的帶狀結構，因而最終形成破碎而不連續的卡氏帶<ref name="pmid28104889">{{cite journal | author=Nakayama, T.; Shinohara, H.; Tanaka, M.; Baba, K.; Ogawa-Ohnishi, M.; Matsubayashi, Y. | title=A peptide hormone required for Casparian strip diffusion barrier formation in Arabidopsis roots. | journal=''Science'' | year=2017 | volume=355 | issue=6322 | pages=284-286 | pmid=28104889 | doi=10.1126/science.aai9057 | pmc= | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=28104889 | access-date=2021-04-17 | archive-date=2021-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417074842/https://science.sciencemag.org/content/355/6322/284.long | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="pmid25233277">{{cite journal | author=Pfister, A.; Barberon, M.; Alassimone, J.; Kalmbach, L.; Lee, Y.; Vermeer, J. E. M. | display-authors=etal | title=A receptor-like kinase mutant with absent endodermal diffusion barrier displays selective nutrient homeostasis defects | journal=''eLife''| year=2014 | volume=3 | issue= | pages=e03115 | pmid=25233277 | doi=10.7554/eLife.03115 | pmc=4164916 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=25233277 | access-date=2021-04-17 | archive-date=2021-04-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417074840/https://elifesciences.org/articles/03115 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

光照、土壤鹽分與缺水逆境等環境因子均會影響卡氏帶的發育<ref name="WuLin2005"/>。

